- Fixed Windows MDM discovery to advertise the `Federated` authentication policy (with Microsoft's enrollment LoginRedirect URL) when a Microsoft Entra tenant is configured, so device-initiated BYOD enrollment via "Access work or school" succeeds instead of failing with `0x80180027`. When no Entra tenant is configured, device-initiated enrollment now returns an actionable error instead of the opaque `0x80180027` failure.
